UseEngine
=========

Mix in engine defined classes in your app classes, for overwriting with custom behaviour.


Example
=======


class FrontendUser < User
  
  use_engine :nc_backend_basics
  
end

class FrontendUser < User
  
  use_engine :nc_backend_basics, :version => '0.4.0', :path => 'models'
  
end



